data.description: Discover your dream home in Edgewood, NM! This stunning 4-bed, 4-bath detached property rests on a sprawling 10-acre lot. Recent renovations include a new roof, stucco, fresh paint, and new mini splits for efficient heating/cooling. The bathrooms boast new shower surrounds and modern vanities, while the kitchen dazzles with stainless steel appliances. Enjoy worry-free living with new water heaters and a septic system upgrade. The vast outdoor space is perfect for gardening, recreation, or keeping horses. Peaceful rural living meets convenience with nearby amenities. Don't miss this meticulously updated home in an idyllic setting! Schedule a showing today.
